{"id":316810,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/10/维权网-浙江省天台县冤妇陆冬菜又被关进黑监狱/","date":"2013-10-07T06:17:48Z","modified":"2013-10-07T06:17:48Z","title":"维权网 | 浙江省天台县冤妇陆冬菜又被关进黑监狱","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span><br /></span></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员黄天怒报道）因丈夫被摩托车撞死，交警处理不公而上访并被判刑的浙江省天台县赤城街道九峰村农妇陆冬菜陆冬菜于<span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">28</span>日被关进天台县政府设在当地的黑监狱“凤雅兰庄”，至今已有<span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span>天，政府雇佣的黑帮分子每天<span lang=\"EN-US\">24</span>小时轮流换班看管。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>去年“十八大”期间天台著名维权人士徐江姣在天安门撒传单被当局抓回后，曾在该黑监狱关了<span lang=\"EN-US\">44</span>天。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>陆冬菜去年“两会”期间被天台县当局关进黑监狱达一年半，直到今天<span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span>月初才放出。<span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span>日她去北京上访，<span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">22</span>日被送进久敬庄，<span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">27</span>日被天台县政府从久敬庄接出，<span lang=\"EN-US\">28</span>日押回天台，当天就被关进“凤雅兰庄”限制陆冬菜的人身自由。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><span>陆冬菜电话：<span lang=\"EN-US\">15268864455</span>。<span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></span></div>\n</div>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910,19196]}